I'm truly sorry!

00:28:02.471 --> 00:28:03.431
I won't do it!

00:28:03.431 --> 00:28:05.141
Sorry, I won't do it! Seriously!

00:28:05.141 --> 00:28:07.143
What won't you do? Spell it out!

00:28:07.852 --> 00:28:09.770
I won't kill myself!

00:28:09.770 --> 00:28:11.480
I won't try to kill myself!

00:28:12.565 --> 00:28:13.482
You mean it?

00:28:14.442 --> 00:28:15.568
I mean it!

00:28:16.360 --> 00:28:17.653
Good.

00:28:17.653 --> 00:28:18.821
It's a promise, okay?

00:28:19.989 --> 00:28:20.990
Hey, Mom!

00:28:24.076 --> 00:28:25.244
Ow!

00:28:26.204 --> 00:28:27.538
W-Water!

00:28:36.464 --> 00:28:41.093
<i>I was going to jump off a tall bridge
and die yesterday.</i>

00:28:43.095 --> 00:28:46.766
<i>Going to see Nishimiya was part of it too.</i>

00:28:47.600 --> 00:28:50.561
<i>It was the biggest test of courage in my life.</i>

00:28:51.395 --> 00:28:52.647
<i>But...</i>

00:29:07.536 --> 00:29:08.871
Friends...

