What have I done?

00:29:17.255 --> 00:29:20.258
<i>At our middle school entrance ceremony,
I overheard Shimada say...</i>

00:29:20.967 --> 00:29:24.845
Stay away from a guy named Shoya Ishida.

00:29:25.596 --> 00:29:28.266
