00:31:11.869 --> 00:31:14.455
<i>"Oh, he's looking this way again.</i>

00:31:14.955 --> 00:31:17.833
<i>Doesn't he get lonely, being all alone all the time?</i>

00:31:17.833 --> 00:31:19.126
<i>Will he spend his whole life like that?</i>

00:31:20.002 --> 00:31:21.379
<i>Why does he even live, then?"</i>

00:31:26.801 --> 00:31:28.135
S-Say...

00:31:28.135 --> 00:31:30.429
