00:31:45.277 --> 00:31:46.153
Seriously?

00:32:02.128 --> 00:32:04.630
<i>That hair looks familiar.</i>

00:32:06.173 --> 00:32:07.091
<i>Who was he, again?</i>

00:32:18.310 --> 00:32:19.562
<i>You know...</i>

00:32:19.812 --> 00:32:22.022
<i>Can I really go see Nishimiya again?</i>

00:32:23.107 --> 00:32:25.443
<i>She said she regularly feeds the carp bread.</i>

00:32:26.610 --> 00:32:29.822
<i>But man, who do I think I am?</i>

00:32:32.199 --> 00:32:34.368
<i>Maybe I could go apologize
for making her cry?</i>

00:32:35.828 --> 00:32:38.456
<i>She said she'd be there every Tuesday.</i>

00:32:39.415 --> 00:32:40.583
<i>Would it be creepy?</i>

00:32:53.053 --> 00:32:54.847
I'm back.

00:33:05.566 --> 00:33:07.109
Sho...

00:33:08.194 --> 00:33:09.945
You gave me a start.

00:33:10.362 --> 00:33:11.572
What is it?

00:33:13.657 --> 00:33:15.743
Sorry about this morning.

00:33:16.243 --> 00:33:20.331
For burning all that money you earned.

00:33:22.124 --> 00:33:28.005
But I wouldn't want the money
you earned in order to die, anyway.

00:33:29.798 --> 00:33:30.758
Sorry.

00:33:30.758 --> 00:33:32.134
I'll earn it again.

00:33:32.134 --> 00:33:34.220
My, thank you.

00:33:34.220 --> 00:33:36.430
Take your time.

00:33:36.430 --> 00:33:38.057
You must be starving.

00:33:38.057 --> 00:33:38.974
Come, let's eat.

00:33:38.974 --> 00:33:40.392
