00:34:03.082 --> 00:34:04.124
<i>Oh, it's that guy.</i>

00:34:04.124 --> 00:34:05.918
I forgot something.

00:34:05.918 --> 00:34:07.336
I want to go get it.

00:34:07.336 --> 00:34:09.755
