00:34:17.179 --> 00:34:18.138
Stop it.

00:34:18.138 --> 00:34:19.306
Let go, dude.

00:34:19.306 --> 00:34:20.432
Hey, knock it off.

00:34:20.975 --> 00:34:22.059
