00:34:22.393 --> 00:34:23.102
Dude...

00:34:24.520 --> 00:34:26.772
Anybody!

00:34:26.772 --> 00:34:27.064
Hey!

00:34:27.064 --> 00:34:27.523
Crap!
Hey!

00:34:27.731 --> 00:34:29.066
Help me!

00:34:29.066 --> 00:34:30.693
Keep it down!

00:34:34.071 --> 00:34:35.406
Let go!

00:34:36.073 --> 00:34:37.116
Uh...

00:34:38.742 --> 00:34:40.286
You can take mine.

00:34:40.703 --> 00:34:42.746
For real?

00:34:42.746 --> 00:34:43.956
You're a god.

00:34:48.043 --> 00:34:49.378
<i>I didn't get it back.</i>

00:34:51.255 --> 00:34:53.424
<i>And it just had to happen on a Tuesday.</i>

00:34:54.008 --> 00:34:57.136
<i>Is it a sign that I shouldn't go see her?</i>

00:34:58.304 --> 00:35:00.472
<i>It's not like I can't walk there,</i>

00:35:00.931 --> 00:35:03.100
<i>but I feel like the universe
is telling me not to go.</i>

00:35:04.810 --> 00:35:05.686
<i>I need an excuse...</i>

00:35:05.686 --> 00:35:06.478
Fluffy New Bread Discount Coupon
Miss Baguette <i>I need an excuse...</i>

00:35:06.478 --> 00:35:07.313
Fluffy New Bread Discount
Coupon Miss Baguette

00:35:10.899 --> 00:35:16.280
