00:40:28.258 --> 00:40:30.218
Shithead!

00:40:30.218 --> 00:40:31.303
Hey, look.

00:40:31.303 --> 00:40:32.846
What's going on?

00:40:32.846 --> 00:40:34.139
Isn't that Yuzuru?

00:40:34.139 --> 00:40:34.973
Oh, no.

