Thanks.

01:06:27.107 --> 01:06:28.066
...moo.

01:06:29.276 --> 01:06:30.360
What?

01:06:31.028 --> 01:06:31.612
These?

01:06:34.031 --> 01:06:36.074
...moo.

01:06:46.710 --> 01:06:48.587
I Iub moo!

01:06:58.055 --> 01:06:58.931
Love the moon?

01:07:00.224 --> 01:07:01.058
Yeah.

01:07:02.392 --> 01:07:03.435
It is very pretty today.

01:07:09.733 --> 01:07:10.901
N-Nishimiya?

01:07:14.863 --> 01:07:17.824
Yoohoo! Are you free now? Let's go watch
a movie! From your big friend Nagatsuka

01:07:20.118 --> 01:07:21.411
Say, Nagatsuka.

01:07:21.954 --> 01:07:23.413
Do these look like the moon to you?

01:07:23.872 --> 01:07:26.875
The moon? Not really, no.

01:07:29.545 --> 01:07:29.795
Can

01:07:29.795 --> 01:07:31.880
Doesn't seem like they're candy.

01:07:32.422 --> 01:07:34.800
Nishimiya gave them to me earlier.

01:07:35.342 --> 01:07:37.094
Seriously, what the heck are these?

01:07:43.559 --> 01:07:45.227
Something happen?

01:07:47.980 --> 01:07:49.439
I told Ishida I love him.

01:07:49.439 --> 01:07:50.732
For real?!

01:07:53.860 --> 01:07:55.070
But it didn't get through to him.

01:08:03.036 --> 01:08:05.289
Wow, you changed your hairstyle.

01:08:05.289 --> 01:08:06.623
Why'd you change it?

01:08:06.623 --> 01:08:08.125
Did something happen?

01:08:08.125 --> 01:08:10.294
You look great!

01:08:11.837 --> 01:08:15.048
Cut it out, guys.

01:08:15.257 --> 01:08:17.843
I was just running short on time.

01:08:18.093 --> 01:08:20.721
Really? But it looks nice.

01:08:20.721 --> 01:08:22.556
Hey, Kawai.

01:08:22.889 --> 01:08:24.766
Why'd you change your hairstyle?

01:08:25.058 --> 01:08:27.644
Why, you ask?

01:08:27.644 --> 01:08:30.230
No special reason, really.

01:08:31.565 --> 01:08:34.443
That's how it goes with girls.

01:08:34.818 --> 01:08:35.652
Oh.

01:08:37.404 --> 01:08:38.238
What?

01:08:38.238 --> 01:08:43.869
The other day, Mashiba said
he'd like to be friends with you.

01:08:52.544 --> 01:08:54.546
Why are you here?

01:08:54.921 --> 01:08:57.215
Nice to meet you. I'm Sahara.

01:08:57.215 --> 01:08:58.925
Hello. I'm Mashiba.

01:08:58.925 --> 01:08:59.551
Stop that!

01:08:59.843 --> 01:09:01.470
Don't go over my head!

01:09:01.470 --> 01:09:04.014
Long time no see, Miyo!

01:09:04.014 --> 01:09:06.058
Hey, where's Nishimiya today?

01:09:06.058 --> 01:09:07.768
She went home, saying her tummy hurt.

01:09:09.102 --> 01:09:11.605
Is she avoiding me?

01:09:11.813 --> 01:09:12.689
Why?

01:09:12.689 --> 01:09:18.153
She was trying her best to tell me something
the other day, and I couldn't get it.

01:09:18.153 --> 01:09:20.030
What did she say?

01:09:20.781 --> 01:09:21.615
That she loves the moon.

01:09:22.532 --> 01:09:25.994
They're such simple words,
but I couldn't understand them.

01:09:25.994 --> 01:09:28.789
Oh, that would've pissed her off.

01:09:28.789 --> 01:09:32.834
Well, if you're worried she's avoiding you,
ask her to hang out.

01:09:33.251 --> 01:09:35.420
She'll refuse if she doesn't want to see you.

01:09:36.088 --> 01:09:37.255
Oh...

01:09:41.259 --> 01:09:44.388
Hey... A bunch of us are going
out soon. Wanna come with?

01:09:59.361 --> 01:10:01.905
Let's line up for that one first!

01:10:01.905 --> 01:10:03.448
Follow me, and don't fall behind!

01:10:03.949 --> 01:10:06.076
Why is she taking charge?

01:10:06.076 --> 01:10:07.411
Beats me.

01:10:07.411 --> 01:10:08.328
Ishida.

01:10:09.454 --> 01:10:10.872
What's with her?

01:10:12.332 --> 01:10:14.543
She's acting awfully friendly.

01:10:15.168 --> 01:10:17.212
Ueno? Why?

01:10:18.714 --> 01:10:20.465
Someone Shoko knows?

01:10:20.465 --> 01:10:22.175
Y-Yeah.

01:10:22.175 --> 01:10:24.010
From grade school.

01:10:30.517 --> 01:10:32.102
Can I sit with you, Sahara?

01:10:32.436 --> 01:10:33.562
Sure. Go ahead.

01:10:36.356 --> 01:10:37.816
I'm kinda scared.

01:10:38.275 --> 01:10:40.360
Are you all ready?

01:10:40.360 --> 01:10:41.778
Yeah!

01:10:42.195 --> 01:10:43.739
Here we go, then!

01:10:45.949 --> 01:10:49.453
Are you okay with having Ueno around?

01:10:50.871 --> 01:10:52.038
Oh, yeah.

01:10:52.038 --> 01:10:54.332
We're in the same design course in school.

01:10:55.500 --> 01:10:58.920
I learn so much from her artistic sense.

01:11:00.839 --> 01:11:04.718
When I was in grade school,
I was too scared to ride a roller coaster.

01:11:05.218 --> 01:11:06.678
I was a coward, you see.

01:11:09.181 --> 01:11:12.184
But I tried changing my perspective a little.

01:11:13.477 --> 01:11:17.147
I figured I could decide whether
it was scary or not after I gave it a shot.

01:11:20.066 --> 01:11:21.860
Though I am still terrified.

01:11:23.945 --> 01:11:24.863
Here it comes.

01:11:45.383 --> 01:11:47.928
Oh, no!

01:11:47.928 --> 01:11:49.805
Your legs are all wobbly, Sho.

01:11:52.349 --> 01:11:53.517
Are you okay?

01:11:55.727 --> 01:11:57.062
Wow.

01:11:57.354 --> 01:11:58.772
You know sign language?

01:11:59.022 --> 01:12:01.566
You must've worked hard to pick it up, Ishida.

01:12:06.905 --> 01:12:08.615
Hey! What's with your hand?

01:12:08.990 --> 01:12:11.076
You're being rude to my Yasho!

01:12:11.076 --> 01:12:13.495
What? I'm just trying to be friendly.

01:12:13.495 --> 01:12:15.413
No way! Don't think it's that easy!

01:12:15.413 --> 01:12:17.666
You're funny, Nagatsuka.

01:12:17.999 --> 01:12:21.002
Anyone who wants to approach Yasho
has to go through me!

01:12:21.002 --> 01:12:23.421
Is your hair natural?

01:12:24.422 --> 01:12:26.007
Stop it!

01:12:27.092 --> 01:12:28.176
Don't touch me!

01:12:28.176 --> 01:12:29.177
Huh?

01:12:29.845 --> 01:12:31.847
Run away, Mashiba!

01:12:32.138 --> 01:12:34.057
Go, Yasho! Overtake them!

01:12:34.391 --> 01:12:35.267
<i>Huh?</i>

01:12:36.852 --> 01:12:40.021
<i>Do I have any right to have so much fun?</i>

01:12:41.648 --> 01:12:44.776
<i>But this feels kinda like...</i>

01:12:46.152 --> 01:12:47.362
What are you doing?

01:12:47.696 --> 01:12:52.325
<i>You know, like a group of friends!</i>

01:12:58.039 --> 01:12:58.915
Ishida.

01:13:00.166 --> 01:13:02.252
I want takoyaki.

01:13:02.669 --> 01:13:03.920
Let's go buy some.

01:13:03.920 --> 01:13:06.089
H-Hey, wait.

01:13:07.883 --> 01:13:09.718
Here's your takoyaki.

01:13:10.719 --> 01:13:11.761
Thank you.

01:13:11.761 --> 01:13:13.138
Look, Ueno.

01:13:13.430 --> 01:13:15.390
You don't need to play peacemaker.

01:13:22.063 --> 01:13:22.439
Die
Go away, traitor

01:13:23.899 --> 01:13:26.026
Sh-Shimada?

01:13:31.573 --> 01:13:32.866
Hey, Ishida?

01:13:35.952 --> 01:13:37.537
Sorry! I'll text you!

01:13:39.748 --> 01:13:40.749
Ishida!

01:13:41.708 --> 01:13:42.751
Are you mad?

01:13:43.209 --> 01:13:44.336
I'm not.

01:13:45.295 --> 01:13:46.880
I'm not mad.

01:13:47.339 --> 01:13:53.261
I was just hoping you two
could go back to being friends.

01:13:54.095 --> 01:13:57.724
I figured things would work out if you met.

01:13:58.266 --> 01:13:59.726
Nobody asked you.

01:14:04.105 --> 01:14:04.814
Wait.

01:14:05.815 --> 01:14:07.943
Didn't I do the exact same thing?

01:14:13.156 --> 01:14:15.533
You and I are alike.

01:14:15.533 --> 01:14:16.576
No, we're not.

01:14:17.035 --> 01:14:17.869
Yes, we are.

01:14:18.620 --> 01:14:19.663
No, we're not.

01:14:23.875 --> 01:14:24.459
Hey.

01:14:25.001 --> 01:14:28.421
Everything would've been fine and dandy
if it wasn't for Nishimiya, right?

01:14:30.215 --> 01:14:31.675
We don't know that.

01:14:31.675 --> 01:14:33.134
But I do.

01:14:33.927 --> 01:14:38.848
If she wasn't around, things wouldn't have
gotten awkward between Sahara and me.

01:14:38.848 --> 01:14:41.893
And you and Shimada wouldn't have fallen out.

01:14:42.894 --> 01:14:46.147
I want to back to how things were before she came.

01:14:46.147 --> 01:14:47.565
The thing with Shimada...

01:14:47.941 --> 01:14:50.777
It's all on me.

01:14:51.861 --> 01:14:54.072
Do you hate me?

01:14:54.906 --> 01:14:55.615
Probably.

01:14:57.826 --> 01:15:00.245
I think I want to ride the Ferris wheel.

01:15:00.578 --> 01:15:03.206
I should take Nishimiya.

01:15:03.206 --> 01:15:03.957
Hey.

01:15:05.458 --> 01:15:08.586
Nishimiya, ride the Ferris wheel with me.

01:15:08.586 --> 01:15:10.005
Wait, Ueno.

01:15:10.005 --> 01:15:12.340
Take this with you, Sis.

01:15:13.049 --> 01:15:15.343
I'm riding the roller coaster again.

01:15:38.324 --> 01:15:40.952
Oh, hey. Welcome, Yuzuru.

01:15:40.952 --> 01:15:42.746
Shoya's upstairs.

01:15:44.122 --> 01:15:44.581
Hey.

01:15:45.081 --> 01:15:46.916
I got my hands on some top-secret footage.

01:15:48.209 --> 01:15:49.669
Video of the Ferris wheel?

01:15:50.170 --> 01:15:51.337
Yeah.

01:15:51.337 --> 01:15:53.214
What? How?

01:15:53.506 --> 01:15:54.340
Secretly filmed them.

01:15:59.971 --> 01:16:01.890
Listen.

01:16:02.474 --> 01:16:03.975
I hate you.

01:16:08.354 --> 01:16:09.856
Let's not.

01:16:10.940 --> 01:16:13.735
I'll talk slowly so you can understand,

01:16:13.735 --> 01:16:16.071
and I'll pay attention to what you're saying.

01:16:17.906 --> 01:16:20.325
Back in grade school,

01:16:20.325 --> 01:16:24.162
I had no understanding of you or your situation.

01:16:24.162 --> 01:16:28.917
But you never tried to understand me, either.

01:16:29.417 --> 01:16:33.213
That's why you'd obliviously
hand over your stupid notebook,

01:16:33.213 --> 01:16:35.632
and have a stupid smile on your face all the time.

01:16:35.632 --> 01:16:39.135
And anytime something happened,
you'd immediately apologize.

01:16:39.803 --> 01:16:43.181
So I changed my approach.

01:16:43.181 --> 01:16:47.102
I ignored you and badmouthed you.

01:16:47.102 --> 01:16:51.106
They were signs to stay away from me.

01:16:51.523 --> 01:16:56.111
But instead of picking up on them,
you fired back.

01:16:56.111 --> 01:16:58.029
You went crying to the adults.

01:16:58.947 --> 01:17:02.075
Because of that, Ishida lost all his friends.

01:17:02.534 --> 01:17:06.162
Everything around us fell apart.

01:17:08.498 --> 01:17:10.166
I'm Sowwy.

01:17:10.166 --> 01:17:12.836
It's not like I want you to apologize.

01:17:13.753 --> 01:17:16.256
We were doing everything we could back then,

01:17:16.256 --> 01:17:19.717
and looking back, I even feel like maybe
it was inevitable how things turned out.

01:17:19.717 --> 01:17:24.597
But I'm not about to tell you
we should be friends now.

01:17:24.597 --> 01:17:27.308
I still hate you,

01:17:27.308 --> 01:17:29.352
and you hate me.

01:17:29.978 --> 01:17:33.606
So how about we take it easy from now on?

01:17:33.606 --> 01:17:36.484
Let's shake hands as two people
who hate each other.

01:17:37.318 --> 01:17:40.029
Y-You're wrog.

01:17:40.029 --> 01:17:43.533
I hade mysel.

01:17:45.160 --> 01:17:46.161
What the heck?

01:17:47.328 --> 01:17:48.955
What the hell is up with that?

01:17:52.750 --> 01:17:54.419
So what?

01:17:54.878 --> 01:17:56.963
Are you going to apologize again?

01:17:57.630 --> 01:18:00.884
In the end, things are the same as five years ago.

01:18:00.884 --> 01:18:02.802
You're not even trying to talk to me.

01:18:09.601 --> 01:18:10.643
What do you think?

01:18:11.227 --> 01:18:13.730
Oh, uh...

01:18:16.941 --> 01:18:21.404
I want Nishimiya to come to love herself.

01:18:30.705 --> 01:18:32.749
Ueno, was it?

01:18:32.749 --> 01:18:34.375
What about her?

01:18:35.126 --> 01:18:38.421
Did something happen
between her and Nishimiya?

01:18:38.421 --> 01:18:40.131
Huh? Why do you ask?

01:18:40.131 --> 01:18:43.635
Kawai said things were complicated
in grade school.

01:18:45.261 --> 01:18:49.349
Nishimiya really can't hear, huh?

01:18:50.642 --> 01:18:51.559
Yeah.

01:18:51.559 --> 01:18:55.813
Wait, is that why she was bullied?

01:18:57.690 --> 01:19:01.569
I can't stand stuff like that.

01:19:02.028 --> 01:19:03.863
Don't you agree, Ishida?

01:19:04.614 --> 01:19:06.241
Huh? What do you mean?

01:19:06.658 --> 01:19:09.702
Are you saying I'm going around
telling people about the past?

01:19:09.702 --> 01:19:11.663
Ch-Chill. You're being too loud.

01:19:13.831 --> 01:19:16.668
You haven't changed one bit.

01:19:17.543 --> 01:19:19.629
You were and still are a colossal jerk!

01:19:19.629 --> 01:19:20.338
What's wrong, Yasho?
You were and still are a colossal jerk!

01:19:20.338 --> 01:19:21.047
What's wrong, Yasho?

01:19:21.047 --> 01:19:22.507
Calm down, Kawai.

01:19:23.007 --> 01:19:24.050
What're you talking about?

01:19:24.425 --> 01:19:29.681
Mishiba, Ishida once bullied a girl.

01:19:32.267 --> 01:19:34.227
What are you saying, Kawai?

01:19:34.894 --> 01:19:36.271
That can't be...

01:19:36.271 --> 01:19:37.355
It's true!

01:19:39.315 --> 01:19:41.317
You badmouthed her yourself.

01:19:41.859 --> 01:19:45.071
I never badmouthed Nishimiya.

01:19:45.613 --> 01:19:46.698
Nishimiya?

01:19:46.698 --> 01:19:50.743
That's right! Ishida bullied Nishimiya!

01:19:52.704 --> 01:19:56.207
You know, I tried to stop him.

01:19:57.083 --> 01:19:59.711
But he just wouldn't listen.

01:20:00.253 --> 01:20:02.171
It was so scary.

01:20:04.173 --> 01:20:05.425
Yasho?

01:20:05.925 --> 01:20:07.302
You ok?

01:20:07.302 --> 01:20:09.304
Sorry, Nagatsuka.

01:20:09.304 --> 01:20:10.388
Yasho?

01:20:12.348 --> 01:20:13.641
Yasho!

01:20:42.295 --> 01:20:44.964
<i>Yeah, I hate myself too.</i>

01:20:56.434 --> 01:20:58.436
Oh, Ishida.

01:20:58.436 --> 01:20:59.020
Hey.

01:21:01.230 --> 01:21:02.440
Something wrong?

01:21:03.733 --> 01:21:05.360
N-Nothing.

01:21:06.736 --> 01:21:07.653
Really.

01:21:09.614 --> 01:21:11.366
There you are, Ishida!

01:21:11.741 --> 01:21:13.910
I brought your bag.

01:21:13.910 --> 01:21:14.744
Heya.

01:21:14.744 --> 01:21:16.079
Nao?

01:21:17.080 --> 01:21:18.748
I called her.

01:21:22.585 --> 01:21:24.462
Sorry about earlier.

01:21:25.171 --> 01:21:29.550
But it was all your fault to begin with.

01:21:30.718 --> 01:21:38.142
Still, Mashiba said I should forgive you
if you apologized to Nishimiya.

01:21:38.142 --> 01:21:39.477
Wait a second.

01:21:40.061 --> 01:21:42.188
That's messed up.

01:21:42.188 --> 01:21:45.942
What right do we have to criticize Ishida over it?

01:21:47.235 --> 01:21:48.152
"We"?

01:21:48.820 --> 01:21:50.488
You've got it wrong, Nao.

01:21:50.488 --> 01:21:51.364
Got what wrong?

01:21:52.198 --> 01:21:57.036
Unlike me, you went out of your way
to bully Nishimiya.

01:21:57.286 --> 01:21:59.330
Don't lump me in with you.

01:22:00.665 --> 01:22:01.541
Nao...

01:22:02.708 --> 01:22:03.626
Ah.

01:22:04.460 --> 01:22:06.087
Yeah.

01:22:06.462 --> 01:22:10.383
I'm not like you at all. You just laughed
and fell in line with what I was doing!

01:22:11.926 --> 01:22:12.593
Mean!

01:22:13.094 --> 01:22:14.929
What do you think, Sahara?

01:22:15.596 --> 01:22:16.806
You're asking me?

01:22:16.806 --> 01:22:20.226
Nao badmouthed you a ton too, Sahara!

01:22:20.226 --> 01:22:22.228
I was only telling the truth!

01:22:23.604 --> 01:22:26.190
Out with it, Sahara.

01:22:26.816 --> 01:22:28.734
I-I ...

01:22:29.402 --> 01:22:33.406
I was scared of you both back then.

01:22:33.406 --> 01:22:35.741
What? Whose side are you on?

01:22:35.741 --> 01:22:37.452
Neither of you!

01:22:37.452 --> 01:22:38.327
Enough.

01:22:40.288 --> 01:22:43.374
It's all my fault.

01:22:45.042 --> 01:22:46.878
I hate that line of thinking.

01:22:47.962 --> 01:22:48.838
Ueno.

01:22:50.047 --> 01:22:53.342
Stop thinking you can decide everything for others.

01:22:54.218 --> 01:22:55.887
You don't have to put it like that.

01:22:55.887 --> 01:22:57.430
Shut up, Sahara.

01:22:57.430 --> 01:23:00.641
You're just gonna run and regret
your cowardice again, anyway.

01:23:01.476 --> 01:23:03.227
What's gotten into you, Ishida?

01:23:03.478 --> 01:23:05.605
Not another word, Kawai.

01:23:06.272 --> 01:23:09.817
All you've ever cared about is yourself.

01:23:10.234 --> 01:23:11.402
Yasho...

01:23:11.402 --> 01:23:13.613
I'm on your side, okay.

01:23:14.197 --> 01:23:17.909
Oh, buzz off. You don't know
the first thing about me.

01:23:18.618 --> 01:23:20.995
I've had it! I'm leaving!

01:23:22.205 --> 01:23:23.247
Yasho...

01:23:24.957 --> 01:23:25.875
It's okay.

01:23:26.375 --> 01:23:28.586
It doesn't bother me.

01:23:30.087 --> 01:23:31.130
Sho.

01:23:32.465 --> 01:23:33.424
See you.

01:23:39.931 --> 01:23:41.682
Sorry, Ishida.

01:23:42.850 --> 01:23:45.019
I shouldn't have come.

01:23:48.397 --> 01:23:50.191
Ishida, you're too awful.

01:23:52.652 --> 01:23:55.154
Keep your nose out of it, outsider.

01:23:56.697 --> 01:23:58.449
And here I thought we were friends.

01:24:11.379 --> 01:24:12.421
Right.

01:24:13.464 --> 01:24:17.093
Summer break starts next week.

01:24:17.843 --> 01:24:19.845
Wanna go somewhere...

01:24:36.654 --> 01:24:38.531
I don't care. I'm sorry. Are
you listening to me?! I'm sorry.

01:24:39.073 --> 01:24:40.074
Yuzu?

01:24:41.325 --> 01:24:44.787
Your eyes will go bad if you read in the dark.

01:24:50.418 --> 01:24:51.168
Here.

01:24:58.342 --> 01:25:01.887
Are you still worried about your sister?

01:25:04.557 --> 01:25:07.643
Meanwhile, I'm worried about you.

01:25:07.893 --> 01:25:09.687
All you care about is your sister.

01:25:09.687 --> 01:25:13.065
You're not at all trying to figure out
who you are as a person.

01:25:14.066 --> 01:25:15.985
Like you're any better.

01:25:16.402 --> 01:25:20.281
You're skipping out on the senior citizen
meets to learn sign language.

01:25:20.865 --> 01:25:24.577
I'm doing it for myself, so it doesn't count.

01:25:24.952 --> 01:25:28.414
Then I'm doing it for myself too.

01:25:29.874 --> 01:25:31.083
Is that so?

01:25:34.462 --> 01:25:36.464
You're a good girl.

01:25:37.048 --> 01:25:37.882
You think?

01:25:38.424 --> 01:25:41.260
Mom keeps yelling at me every day.

01:25:41.260 --> 01:25:43.220
I haven't gone to school in forever, too.

01:25:43.763 --> 01:25:46.057
Your heart is pure.

01:25:46.932 --> 01:25:48.768
Shoko's hanging in there too.

01:25:51.145 --> 01:25:54.774
I've been blessed with
truly amazing granddaughters.

01:25:58.653 --> 01:26:00.529
Have some steamed buns.

01:26:00.529 --> 01:26:01.739
I will.

01:26:16.587 --> 01:26:17.505
Grandma...

01:26:30.226 --> 01:26:32.228
Hey, Nishimiya. How are you doing?

01:26:32.645 --> 01:26:37.274
I got some really nice bread today.

01:26:37.858 --> 01:26:39.485
This bread...

01:26:41.487 --> 01:26:44.740
It's good, like you.

01:26:44.740 --> 01:26:45.783
So...

01:26:47.326 --> 01:26:48.577
What the heck?

01:26:49.870 --> 01:26:50.496
Huh?

01:26:52.498 --> 01:26:54.041
Isn't she coming today?

01:26:57.461 --> 01:26:58.462
Er...

01:26:59.046 --> 01:27:01.340
Do you have another stomach ache?

01:27:02.258 --> 01:27:03.342
Wait, that's weird.

01:27:13.185 --> 01:27:15.396
Hey, Yuzu !

01:27:29.285 --> 01:27:30.161
Guess I'll go home.

01:27:30.161 --> 01:27:31.120
Ishida.

01:27:32.413 --> 01:27:32.997
Heya.

01:27:33.456 --> 01:27:35.040
What's with that outfit?

01:27:35.040 --> 01:27:37.293
It's a uniform, obviously.

01:27:37.293 --> 01:27:38.836
How do I look?

01:27:38.836 --> 01:27:39.879
Why?

01:27:39.879 --> 01:27:41.088
School, duh.

01:27:42.548 --> 01:27:44.800
Aren't we on summer break right now?

01:27:47.219 --> 01:27:48.929
Seriously, what's up?

01:27:51.182 --> 01:27:52.433
Nothing.

01:27:52.892 --> 01:27:55.436
If I had to say, I'm in cosplay.

01:27:58.564 --> 01:28:01.275
It's from Sis. Gotta go.

01:28:01.275 --> 01:28:02.777
I'll walk you. Where to?

01:28:02.777 --> 01:28:03.986
You don't have to.

01:28:04.361 --> 01:28:05.279
Let me.

01:28:05.279 --> 01:28:06.864
Really, you don't have to.

01:28:07.615 --> 01:28:09.283
I saw you crying earlier.

01:28:10.242 --> 01:28:10.951
Why?

01:28:13.579 --> 01:28:15.831
It doesn't have anything to do with you.

01:28:17.458 --> 01:28:20.628
It does, or so I'd like to think.

01:28:21.003 --> 01:28:21.796
And why is that?

01:28:22.713 --> 01:28:24.256
Because I'm worried about you.

01:28:26.383 --> 01:28:28.844
Don't start talking like my grandma.

01:28:31.472 --> 01:28:33.098
Do whatever you want.

01:28:37.019 --> 01:28:38.437
Thanks, Ishida.

01:28:39.021 --> 01:28:41.982
I'll be fine from here.

01:28:41.982 --> 01:28:44.652
Ito Nishimiya Funeral

01:28:44.652 --> 01:28:45.069
Later.
Ito Nishimiya Funeral

01:28:51.617 --> 01:28:53.160
Hang in there, Yuzuru.

01:28:56.872 --> 01:28:57.790
Ishida.

01:29:02.002 --> 01:29:03.671
I'm still scared.

01:30:03.188 --> 01:30:05.900
Hey, Nishimiya.
Would you like to go somewhere tomorrow?

01:30:59.161 --> 01:31:00.996
Awesome!

01:31:03.666 --> 01:31:05.542
Let's go check it out.

01:31:15.260 --> 01:31:16.220
Nishimiya?

01:31:24.979 --> 01:31:26.146
That scared me.

01:31:29.191 --> 01:31:30.359
Why are you apologizing?

01:31:37.074 --> 01:31:38.409
Of course not!

01:31:38.951 --> 01:31:42.371
Say, let's hang out tomorrow too.

01:31:42.371 --> 01:31:43.956
Okay, Nishimiya?

01:31:47.918 --> 01:31:52.506
<i>She said I'd end up unhappy if I was with her.</i>

01:31:54.675 --> 01:31:58.929
<i>This, to the root cause of her unhappiness.</i>

01:32:07.438 --> 01:32:11.650
I wanna see the ocean.

01:32:12.901 --> 01:32:17.239
I wanna love people.

01:32:18.407 --> 01:32:24.371
Even monsters have hearts...

01:32:28.500 --> 01:32:30.711
I don't feel like I can ever fix this.

01:32:35.424 --> 01:32:36.175
Hey, Nishimiya!

01:32:36.425 --> 01:32:39.011
Oh, Yuzuru's coming today? Great!

01:32:39.261 --> 01:32:40.596
Shall we go watch a movie?

01:32:41.889 --> 01:32:43.474
This is great!

01:32:43.891 --> 01:32:44.349
Hey.

01:32:44.808 --> 01:32:45.934
I'm here.

01:32:46.435 --> 01:32:49.730
Man, best summer break ever!

01:32:49.730 --> 01:32:50.856
Right, Yuzuru?

01:32:50.856 --> 01:32:51.732
Don't ask me.

01:32:51.732 --> 01:32:54.401
I'm really enjoying my time, seriously.

01:32:54.401 --> 01:32:55.652
Hey, Nishimiya.

01:32:55.652 --> 01:32:57.404
Where are we going tomorrow?

01:32:57.404 --> 01:32:59.031
We should totally go somewhere.

01:32:59.031 --> 01:33:01.742
Not tomorrow. We have plans.

01:33:02.367 --> 01:33:02.701
What?

01:33:04.661 --> 01:33:06.413
Are you crazy?!

01:33:06.413 --> 01:33:06.997
What are you making?
Are you crazy?!

01:33:06.997 --> 01:33:07.664
What are you making?

01:33:08.040 --> 01:33:09.249
Are you sure about this?

01:33:09.666 --> 01:33:11.877
Should I really be here?

01:33:11.877 --> 01:33:16.590
Your mission is to help us bake
a birthday cake for our mother.

01:33:16.590 --> 01:33:19.343
A-Are you really, really sure?

01:33:19.343 --> 01:33:21.136
Won't I get slapped again?

01:33:21.136 --> 01:33:23.847
Uh, forget slapped. You might get killed.

01:33:23.847 --> 01:33:25.349
Hey...

01:33:25.349 --> 01:33:28.393
That looks great!

01:33:30.437 --> 01:33:31.480
What are you doing?

01:33:31.814 --> 01:33:33.816
Why is this boy here, Shoko?

01:33:33.816 --> 01:33:35.067
What are you trying to pull?

01:33:35.067 --> 01:33:36.026
There, there, Mom.
Get out.

01:33:36.026 --> 01:33:37.402
There, there, Mom.

01:33:37.402 --> 01:33:40.114
What's the big deal? It's a happy occasion.

01:33:40.114 --> 01:33:41.406
Yuzuru.

01:33:41.406 --> 01:33:42.449
You look good.

01:33:49.915 --> 01:33:51.250
Yum!

01:33:51.667 --> 01:33:54.336
Looks like you avoided getting killed, Ishida.

01:33:54.586 --> 01:33:55.879
Y-Yeah.

01:33:55.879 --> 01:33:57.798
We did it, Sis.

01:33:57.798 --> 01:33:59.550
By the way, Yuzuru.

01:33:59.883 --> 01:34:03.428
I picked a photo and submitted it
to the prefectural photography contest.

01:34:03.428 --> 01:34:05.013
Wait, what?

01:34:05.013 --> 01:34:06.807
Sho said you should take part.

01:34:10.686 --> 01:34:13.689
What? They're all weird photos.

01:34:13.689 --> 01:34:15.274
That's not what I found.

01:34:16.400 --> 01:34:18.986
Who asked you two?

01:34:19.903 --> 01:34:20.737
Oh, right.

01:34:21.113 --> 01:34:23.824
There's a fireworks show next Tuesday, Ishida.

01:34:26.285 --> 01:34:27.911
Nah, I'll pass.

01:34:27.911 --> 01:34:29.371
Come on. Let's go.

01:34:42.342 --> 01:34:43.552
Will this do?

01:34:43.552 --> 01:34:44.553
Yeah.

01:35:13.498 --> 01:35:16.335
Oh, I'll go get some yakisoba.

01:35:16.335 --> 01:35:17.419
Come with me, Mom.

01:35:29.598 --> 01:35:30.515
Thanks.

01:35:31.308 --> 01:35:35.395
Oh, and thank you for
inviting me over the other day.

01:35:35.395 --> 01:35:36.605
Was your mother...

01:35:36.605 --> 01:35:39.691
Yeah. You think she was happy?

01:35:39.691 --> 01:35:41.568
I couldn't tell from her poker face.

01:35:42.236 --> 01:35:45.906
When is your birthday?

01:35:47.532 --> 01:35:49.910
June 7th?

01:35:49.910 --> 01:35:52.287
It already passed!

01:35:52.287 --> 01:35:55.791
So you're already eighteen, huh?

01:35:56.458 --> 01:36:00.504
Let's celebrate your nineteenth together, okay?

01:36:00.504 --> 01:36:02.798
I went and said "together"!

01:36:27.489 --> 01:36:30.033
Oh, is that so?

01:36:31.535 --> 01:36:32.911
I see...

01:36:35.414 --> 01:36:36.373
What's up?

01:36:41.503 --> 01:36:44.673
But the show isn't over yet.

01:36:47.217 --> 01:36:48.218
You need to study?

01:36:49.636 --> 01:36:50.804
Oh, okay.

01:36:51.221 --> 01:36:53.557
I'll walk you.

01:36:54.933 --> 01:36:55.726
But...

01:37:02.399 --> 01:37:03.525
All right.

01:37:03.525 --> 01:37:05.152
See you.

01:37:15.412 --> 01:37:16.455
Huh?

01:37:16.913 --> 01:37:18.248
Where's Sis?

01:37:19.207 --> 01:37:20.834
That reminds me, Ishida.

01:37:20.834 --> 01:37:22.544
Could you go get my camera for me?

01:37:37.309 --> 01:37:39.102
Pardon me...

01:37:39.102 --> 01:37:40.479
Whoa, it's dark.

01:37:40.479 --> 01:37:42.189
Nishimiya?

01:37:42.189 --> 01:37:43.732
I'm coming in.

01:37:44.816 --> 01:37:46.068
There it is.

01:37:46.443 --> 01:37:49.154
Is it charged?

01:37:50.572 --> 01:37:52.157
You can see the fireworks from here...?

01:37:53.658 --> 01:37:55.952
Oh, she is here.

01:37:57.829 --> 01:37:58.622
Nishimiya?

01:37:59.623 --> 01:38:00.290
Nishimiya?

01:38:01.291 --> 01:38:03.251
W-W-Wait a second.

01:38:03.668 --> 01:38:05.921
What are you doing, Nishimiya?

01:38:09.883 --> 01:38:10.550
Nishimiya?

01:38:22.813 --> 01:38:23.438
Nishimiya!

01:38:30.612 --> 01:38:31.822
Nishimiya!

01:38:34.116 --> 01:38:35.742
Shoko!

01:38:59.516 --> 01:39:01.059
Why...

01:39:01.059 --> 01:39:02.686
Why, Nishimiya?

01:39:07.649 --> 01:39:10.026
Nishimiya, grab the ledge!

01:39:10.986 --> 01:39:11.820
<i>I beg you, God.</i>

01:39:13.071 --> 01:39:16.450
<i>Please give mo one lest ounce of strength.</i>

01:39:18.076 --> 01:39:20.412
<i>I won't run away from things anymore.</i>

01:39:21.705 --> 01:39:23.123
<i>From tomorrow,</i>

01:39:23.498 --> 01:39:25.584
<i>I'll look at people's faces.</i>

01:39:26.501 --> 01:39:30.046
<i>From tomorrow, I'll listen to their voices.</i>

01:39:31.465 --> 01:39:34.468
<i>From tomorrow, I promise to do things right.</i>

01:39:35.385 --> 01:39:37.387
Nishimiya...

01:39:39.306 --> 01:39:42.476
<i>I gave her that scar back then.</i>

01:39:43.560 --> 01:39:45.562
<i>Did I ever actually apologize to her?</i>

01:39:47.063 --> 01:39:47.939
<i>Sorry.</i>

01:39:48.523 --> 01:39:49.983
<i>I'm sorry, Nishimiya.</i>

01:39:50.901 --> 01:39:52.194
<i>Are you still mad?</i>

01:39:52.819 --> 01:39:55.238
<i>Man, I really messed up.</i>

01:39:55.822 --> 01:40:00.202
<i>I should've asked her how she felt about me.</i>

01:40:01.661 --> 01:40:03.163
<i>By the way, Nishimiya.</i>

01:40:04.206 --> 01:40:04.873
<i>You see, I...</i>

01:40:17.886 --> 01:40:18.845
Sho.

01:40:19.137 --> 01:40:22.140
Your sister made pancakes.

01:40:22.599 --> 01:40:24.768
I'm gonna see the fireworks!

01:40:37.197 --> 01:40:38.406
<i>So cold...</i>

01:40:39.491 --> 01:40:40.784
<i>Yet so warm...</i>

01:40:51.878 --> 01:40:53.588
Suimon Municipal Hospital

01:41:07.060 --> 01:41:07.852
Auntie!

01:41:08.728 --> 01:41:10.397
Oh, Yuzuru.

01:41:11.398 --> 01:41:12.482
I finally got to see you.

01:41:13.024 --> 01:41:15.360
I called the shop, but nobody answered.

01:41:15.360 --> 01:41:17.529
And the hospital said no visits.

01:41:18.613 --> 01:41:20.615
Oh, you can see him now.

01:41:20.615 --> 01:41:22.492
They moved him to a ward room today.

01:41:22.951 --> 01:41:25.745
Come with me. Let him see your face.

01:41:26.413 --> 01:41:28.248
You see, Shoko...

01:41:28.248 --> 01:41:28.999
Ishida.

01:41:30.208 --> 01:41:31.209
Nishimiya?

01:41:32.961 --> 01:41:35.839
Uh, I'm very sorry.

01:41:35.839 --> 01:41:39.092
We caused you trouble once again.

01:41:40.135 --> 01:41:41.720
I'm truly sorry.

01:41:41.720 --> 01:41:42.721
Please don't!

01:41:43.305 --> 01:41:46.474
I'm sure my son did something to Shoko again.

01:41:46.474 --> 01:41:47.225
Otherwise...

01:41:47.225 --> 01:41:51.521
Auntie, he saved my stupid sister.

01:41:52.063 --> 01:41:54.566
I was too negligent.

01:41:55.066 --> 01:41:56.359
I'm sorry.

01:41:59.487 --> 01:42:00.488
Please...

01:42:01.656 --> 01:42:03.450
Please raise your head.

01:42:04.034 --> 01:42:06.369
I'm just glad Shoko's all right.

01:42:06.995 --> 01:42:09.331
You too, Yuzuru.

01:42:10.290 --> 01:42:11.583
Please, I beg you.

01:42:13.168 --> 01:42:16.421
Why did Ishida have to get hurt?!

01:42:17.339 --> 01:42:19.633
Quit trying to be some tragic heroine!

01:42:21.051 --> 01:42:22.385
Say something.

01:42:22.927 --> 01:42:27.432
"I caused everyone trouble
and was really hurt by it,

01:42:27.432 --> 01:42:29.726
so I tried to commit suicide.

01:42:29.726 --> 01:42:31.394
I'm sorry," huh?

01:42:32.103 --> 01:42:33.605
Who the hell do you think you are?

01:42:34.439 --> 01:42:37.609
You're a cancer, Nishimiya.

01:42:38.026 --> 01:42:42.447
People like you, who can only see things
from their own point of view,

01:42:42.447 --> 01:42:44.282
piss me off the most!

01:42:50.205 --> 01:42:51.748
And who the hell are you?!

01:42:55.377 --> 01:42:58.046
Are you her mother?!

01:42:58.421 --> 01:42:59.005
Stop...

01:42:59.005 --> 01:43:02.592
Don't have kids if you can't take care of them!

01:43:02.592 --> 01:43:03.385
What are you doing?

01:43:05.261 --> 01:43:06.471
Stop it.

01:43:09.140 --> 01:43:10.308
Stop it!

01:43:10.850 --> 01:43:11.768
Why?

01:43:12.644 --> 01:43:13.937
What is wrong with you two?

01:43:26.116 --> 01:43:27.951
Are you Shoko?

01:43:31.079 --> 01:43:33.415
Soww...

01:43:34.582 --> 01:43:36.084
I'm Sowwy...

01:43:38.169 --> 01:43:40.088
I'm so Sowwy!

01:43:43.258 --> 01:43:44.759
I'm so Sowwy!

01:43:49.514 --> 01:43:52.308
I'm so Sowwy!

01:44:05.447 --> 01:44:06.656
What are you doing?

01:44:07.949 --> 01:44:12.996
I used to think Sis would stop talking about
wanting to die if she saw these.

01:44:17.500 --> 01:44:19.127
What was I supposed to do?

01:45:08.384 --> 01:45:09.594
It's not opening.

01:45:09.594 --> 01:45:11.012
She's holding it shut!

01:45:11.304 --> 01:45:13.807
Oh, didn't see you there, Nishimiya.

01:45:13.807 --> 01:45:17.018
Shall we head someplace else?
I'll get you a drink.

01:45:18.311 --> 01:45:20.396
I heard about what happened with Yasho.

01:45:23.233 --> 01:45:26.194
I destroyed everything Ishida had built up

01:45:26.528 --> 01:45:28.905
You mean what happened at the bridge?

01:45:30.073 --> 01:45:34.202
Yasho accepted a weirdo like me.

01:45:34.619 --> 01:45:39.249
He made me realize for the first time
what a best friend was.

01:45:43.753 --> 01:45:49.175
Yasho's my big friend,
so I really need him to wake up.

01:45:57.058 --> 01:46:00.812
I want to fix what I destroyed

01:46:06.609 --> 01:46:09.404
Trying to kill yourself 'cause
you're having a hard time is messed up!

01:46:09.779 --> 01:46:12.198
Kawai, you're being too loud.

01:46:12.198 --> 01:46:16.369
She won't hear me unless I yell!

01:46:18.329 --> 01:46:20.540
We were so worried!

01:46:21.040 --> 01:46:24.419
Everyone goes through difficulties in life.

01:46:24.919 --> 01:46:27.213
But we're all in the same boat, aren't we?

01:46:27.213 --> 01:46:33.720
You have to learn to love even the things
you hate about yourself and move forward.

01:46:37.724 --> 01:46:39.475
I'm glad you're all right.

01:46:40.977 --> 01:46:42.937
I want to fix what I destroyed

01:46:42.937 --> 01:46:43.938
I see.
I want to fix what I destroyed

01:46:44.230 --> 01:46:46.649
You went and saw everyone, huh?

01:46:46.858 --> 01:46:47.901
You're strong.

01:46:50.361 --> 01:46:53.114
I'm not as strong as you.

01:46:53.740 --> 01:47:00.371
Even when Ishida does wake up,
I won't know how to face him.

01:47:00.663 --> 01:47:03.458
I couldn't change.

01:47:03.917 --> 01:47:06.169
I failed to protect you again!

01:47:06.419 --> 01:47:07.921
I'm still the same old coward.

01:47:09.714 --> 01:47:11.841
You gan jange from now,

01:47:14.010 --> 01:47:15.595
Tahada...

01:47:18.723 --> 01:47:21.309
Thank you for coming, Sho.

01:48:03.851 --> 01:48:06.521
Jeez, cut that out.

01:48:15.446 --> 01:48:16.990
Nishimiya.

01:48:17.699 --> 01:48:19.867
Found you.

01:48:20.410 --> 01:48:23.871
How are you doing?

01:48:24.580 --> 01:48:25.748
You know,

01:48:26.207 --> 01:48:28.876
this is kinda weird, huh?

01:48:29.335 --> 01:48:30.253
I ...

01:48:30.586 --> 01:48:32.755
wanted to die...

01:48:33.423 --> 01:48:34.382
Oh.

01:48:34.966 --> 01:48:37.635
Tuesday will be over soon.

01:48:38.344 --> 01:48:40.013
Later,

01:48:40.096 --> 01:48:41.055
Nishimiya.

01:49:45.203 --> 01:49:46.079
Nihimiya!

01:49:49.457 --> 01:49:50.333
What's all this?

01:49:51.417 --> 01:49:52.460
Mom?

01:49:52.460 --> 01:49:54.962
Get this crap off me!

01:50:03.262 --> 01:50:04.347
Nishimiya...

01:50:06.891 --> 01:50:08.059
Nishimiya.

01:50:17.026 --> 01:50:18.027
Nishimiya...

01:50:18.820 --> 01:50:19.904
Nishimiya...

01:50:22.824 --> 01:50:24.325
Nishimiya...

01:50:38.923 --> 01:50:39.799
Hey.

01:51:22.967 --> 01:51:23.885
Are you okay?

01:51:30.474 --> 01:51:31.142
Great.

01:51:32.518 --> 01:51:35.813
I'm glad you're fine.

01:51:40.359 --> 01:51:41.360
Nishimiya,

01:51:41.736 --> 01:51:44.405
I'm all good now.

01:51:45.823 --> 01:51:47.116
More or less.

01:51:49.410 --> 01:51:52.705
Come on. Don't cry.

01:51:53.331 --> 01:51:54.415
Oh, right.

01:51:57.793 --> 01:51:58.920
Nishimiya,

01:52:01.172 --> 01:52:02.590
I'm sorry.

01:52:03.257 --> 01:52:07.720
I hadn't actually apologized to you
for what I did to you in the past.

01:52:08.971 --> 01:52:13.351
Or everything after that, either.

